<h1>FILE 2: SCRIPT DAN UI FRONT END</h1>
<p><strong>Sistem Informasi UMKM Berkah Alam</strong></p>
<p>Dokumen ini menyajikan rincian rute, struktur visual layout, katalog produk, form pesanan kustom, dan antarmuka unggah pembayaran bagi customer pada website Berkah Alam.</p>

<hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 18pt 0;" />

<h2>1. Rute Navigasi Front End</h2>
<p>Laravel mendaftarkan route-route Front End dalam berkas <code>routes/web.php</code> sebagai berikut:</p>
<table>
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th style="width: 20%;">URL/Endpoint</th>
            <th style="width: 30%;">Controller & Method</th>
            <th style="width: 35%;">Keterangan</th>
            <th style="width: 15%;">Hak Akses</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td><code>/</code></td>
            <td><code>LandingPageController@index</code></td>
            <td>Katalog, promo hero, galeri pengerjaan, testimoni.</td>
            <td>Publik</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><code>/login</code></td>
            <td><code>AuthController@showLogin</code></td>
            <td>Halaman formulir masuk.</td>
            <td>Guest</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><code>/register</code></td>
            <td><code>AuthController@showRegister</code></td>
            <td>Halaman formulir pendaftaran customer.</td>
            <td>Guest</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><code>/customer/produk/{id}</code></td>
            <td><code>OrderController@showProductDetail</code></td>
            <td>Form kustom ukiran pahat batu nisan/prasasti.</td>
            <td>Customer</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><code>/customer/pesanan/{id}/pembayaran</code></td>
            <td><code>CustomerController@uploadPaymentForm</code></td>
            <td>Form pengunggahan slip transfer bukti bayar.</td>
            <td>Customer</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 18pt 0;" />

<h2>2. Struktur Master Layout (`resources/views/layouts/app.blade.php`)</h2>
<p>Master template mengintegrasikan Bootstrap 5 dengan desain modern agar responsif dan bersih.</p>

<pre><code>&lt;!-- resources/views/layouts/app.blade.php --&gt;
&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang="id"&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;@yield('title', 'BERKAH ALAM')&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS --&gt;
    &lt;link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"&gt;
    &lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.2/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css"&gt;
    &lt;style&gt;
        :root {
            --primary-color: #1A1A1A;
            --accent-color: #C5A059; /* Rich Champagne Gold */
            --background-color: #F8F9FA;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7) !important;
            backdrop-filter: blur(25px); /* Efek Kaca Glassmorphism */
        }
    &lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    @include('layouts.navbar')

    &lt;main class="py-4"&gt;
        @yield('content')
    &lt;/main&gt;

    @include('layouts.footer')
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>

<hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 18pt 0;" />

<h2>3. Katalog Grid Produk (`resources/views/welcome.blade.php`)</h2>
<p>Menyajikan katalog produk batu alam secara elegan dalam bentuk kartu grid responsif.</p>

<pre><code>&lt;!-- welcome.blade.php --&gt;
&lt;div class="row g-4" id="produk"&gt;
    @foreach($products as $product)
        &lt;div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"&gt;
            &lt;div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden"&gt;
                &lt;img src="{{ asset($product->gambar) }}" class="card-img-top" style="height: 280px; object-fit: cover;"&gt;
                &lt;div class="card-body p-4"&gt;
                    &lt;span class="badge bg-secondary-subtle text-dark px-3 py-2 rounded-pill"&gt;
                        {{ $product->kategori->nama }}
                    &lt;/span&gt;
                    &lt;h5 class="fw-bold mt-2"&gt;{{ $product->nama }}&lt;/h5&gt;
                    &lt;p class="text-stone-accent fw-bold fs-5 mt-2"&gt;
                        Rp {{ number_format($product->harga, 0, ',', '.') }}
                    &lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;a href="{{ route('customer.produk.detail', $product->id) }}" class="btn btn-stone-outline w-100 mt-3"&gt;
                        Detail & Pesan Kustom
                    &lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    @endforeach
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>

<hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 18pt 0;" />

<h2>4. Form Kustomisasi Detail Produk (`customer/produk_detail.blade.php`)</h2>
<p>Menangkap masukan kustom teks pahat nisan (Nama Alm., Tanggal Lahir, Tanggal Wafat, Bin/Binti) dan alamat pengantaran.</p>

<pre><code>&lt;!-- customer/produk_detail.blade.php --&gt;
&lt;form method="POST" action="{{ route('customer.order.store', $product->id) }}"&gt;
    @csrf
    
    &lt;!-- Input Jumlah Pcs --&gt;
    &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="qty" class="form-label font-semibold"&gt;Jumlah Pesanan (Pcs)&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="number" name="qty" id="qty" class="form-control" value="1" min="1" max="{{ $product->stok }}" required&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;!-- Teks Kaligrafi / Pahatan Nisan --&gt;
    &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="catatan_ukiran" class="form-label font-semibold"&gt;Teks Ukiran Nisan / Prasasti&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;textarea name="catatan_ukiran" id="catatan_ukiran" class="form-control" rows="4" 
                  placeholder="Contoh:&#10;Nama: Alm. Ahmad Fauzi&#10;Lahir: Jakarta, 12 Jan 1960&#10;Wafat: Bandung, 24 Feb 2024"&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;!-- Alamat Kirim Batu Nisan --&gt;
    &lt;div class="mb-4"&gt;
        &lt;label for="alamat" class="form-label font-semibold"&gt;Alamat Pengiriman&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;textarea name="alamat" id="alamat" class="form-control" rows="3" required&gt;{{ Auth::user()->address }}&lt;/textarea&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;button type="submit" class="btn btn-stone-accent w-100 py-3"&gt;
        &lt;i class="bi bi-cart-plus me-2"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Buat Pesanan Sekarang
    &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>

<hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 18pt 0;" />

<h2>5. Form Unggah Slip Pembayaran (`customer/pembayaran.blade.php`)</h2>
<p>Formulir transfer bank untuk divalidasi oleh administrator.</p>

<div class="alert">
    <strong>PENTING:</strong> Atribut <code>enctype="multipart/form-data"</code> wajib disertakan pada tag <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> agar file bukti transfer dapat dikirimkan ke server backend Laravel.
</div>

<pre><code>&lt;!-- customer/pembayaran.blade.php --&gt;
&lt;form method="POST" action="{{ route('customer.pembayaran.store', $order->id) }}" enctype="multipart/form-data"&gt;
    @csrf
    
    &lt;div class="mb-4"&gt;
        &lt;label for="bukti_pembayaran" class="form-label fw-semibold"&gt;Pilih File Foto Bukti Pembayaran&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="file" name="bukti_pembayaran" id="bukti_pembayaran" class="form-control" required accept="image/*"&gt;
        &lt;span class="form-text text-muted"&gt;Format file: JPG, JPEG, atau PNG.&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;button type="submit" class="btn btn-stone-accent w-100 py-3"&gt;
        &lt;i class="bi bi-send-fill"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Kirim Bukti Pembayaran
    &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>

</body>
</html>
